wheight=\"1624\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-439e88ead3e03e8d2838e49b3dbe0ddd_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"750\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-c3cf438ed4964c66a4c0903fb33b8c9f_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='750'%20height='1624'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"750\" data-rawheight=\"1624\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-439e88ead3e03e8d2838e49b3dbe0ddd_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"750\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-c3cf438ed4964c66a4c0903fb33b8c9f_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-c3cf438ed4964c66a4c0903fb33b8c9f_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559398436,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"a470231887c9ddccf11cc96c7edae05b","url_token":"li-quan-hui-81","name":"叶泉","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-437a6d827c625241dddd139a2855ae21_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-437a6d827c625241dddd139a2855ae21_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/a470231887c9ddccf11cc96c7edae05b","user_type":"people","headline":"车辆硕士/BMS","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559398436","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545723595,"updated_time":1545723595,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":10,"content":"\u003cp\u003e首先你得明白哥猜要证明什么，。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560370252,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560370252","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545832552,"updated_time":1545832552,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":36,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我回答的时候看到的题目是“如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？”，没有看到更详细的描述。下面充斥清一色的冷嘲热讽，好不欢乐。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我要支持一下高中生的勇气，以防止他因为心灰意冷而丧失了对数学生涯的追求。现实中做数学研究你得适应失败。谁还没有个痴心妄想的时候呢，治疗虚妄的良药是阅读，交流，向领域内大师学习。即便在别人看来你提的问题很傻，是错误荒谬的，不要停止提问。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e之所以能提出这样的问题，我觉得很大程度上是因为国内数学科普做得还不够好，以至于连一个热爱数学的高中生都没有意识到哥德巴赫猜想这个问题的难度。在数学中，这种问题属于容易读懂，但证明起来特别复杂。类似于哥德巴赫猜想的问题还有费马大定理[1]等。最好的结果——被清华北大数学系保送，此结果为你从事数学研究继而成为数学家铺平了道路，那数学家群体是怎么看待这个问题的呢？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cblockquote\u003eThis problem has the great virtue of being easy to\u003cbr\u003eunderstand, which makes it appealing in the way that\u003cbr\u003efermat’s last theorem [V.12] and goldbach’s conjecture\u003cbr\u003e[V.30] are appealing. And yet, it is not a central\u003cbr\u003eproblem in the way that those two are: most mathematicians\u003cbr\u003ewould put it into a mental box marked\u003cbr\u003e“recreational” and forget about it.[2]\u003c/blockquote\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e[1]这个问题从提出到解决花了\u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fermat%2527s_Last_Theorem\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003e358\u003c/a\u003e年的时间，有中译本的\u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//baike.baidu.com/item/%25E8%25B4%25B9%25E9%25A9%25AC%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AE%259A%25E7%2590%2586%25EF%25BC%259A%25E4%25B8%2580%25E4%25B8%25AA%25E5%259B%25B0%25E6%2583%2591%25E4%25BA%2586%25E4%25B8%2596%25E9%2597%25B4%25E6%2599%25BA%25E8%2580%2585358%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%259A%2584%25E8%25B0%259C/5549385\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003e科普读物\u003c/a\u003e。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e[2]\u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Princeton_Companion_to_Mathematics\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003eThe Princeton Companion to Mathematics\u003c/a\u003e 第71页。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e[3]陶哲轩关于大问题的\u003ca href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//terrytao.wordpress.com/career-advice/dont-prematurely-obsess-on-a-single-big-problem-or-big-theory/\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"\u003e人生经验\u003c/a\u003e。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561040981,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"d99e0e5ab62a35300a30bf65db03e7ca","url_token":"lu-jun-jiang-87","name":"鲁唧鸡","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-82bc1a9231977c61857cace9cb381393_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-82bc1a9231977c61857cace9cb381393_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/d99e0e5ab62a35300a30bf65db03e7ca","user_type":"people","headline":"大学生，电脑硬件发烧友","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561040981","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545910447,"updated_time":1545910447,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":9,"content":"\u003cp\u003e经常有高中生过来问我，高中生证明哥德巴赫猜想到底能不能保送清华北大啊？我看有些教材，哥德巴赫竟然和黎曼谈起了恋爱，黎曼叫哥德巴赫叫赫赫，哥德巴赫叫黎曼叫曼曼，素数不分，筛分颠倒。这样的教材主创人员是要向全国人民谢罪的！戏说不是胡说，哥猜不是瞎猜。有时候初等数论比筛分法好用，我用裂项相减从1+c推导到1+2，我太了解它了！我们说一个高中生没有自己的理想是可悲的，有了理想还不去奋斗就是可耻的。年轻的网友还在笑，我是笑不出来。有的网友一看到哥猜，第一反应“哇，太难了！”这怎么行呢？要证明哥猜，尤其需要乐观向上。你说你数学比我好，有本事上台比划比划。我是身经百战见得多了，我研究了十七年的高中数学，每年进步不到6分，十七年下来除了数学一本线都考不到。我说高中数学题目你一题都没有做过的请举手，结果没有一个人举手，什么叫做国际imo大佬啊（后仰）？明年1月1日0点，我证明的哥德巴赫猜想论文就要在知乎上发布，我继续担任偏科的天才学生，弘扬中国高中生刻苦钻研的传统文化，继续塑造最新的新时代高中生形象，文理两开花，希望大家多多关注！\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560702729,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"81a939e058786b6db7cf322b6ba78a43","url_token":"ni-ning-tian-kong","name":"泥泞天空","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/1dc3c0bb43162b6863dac9cfdac32488_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/1dc3c0bb43162b6863dac9cfdac32488_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/81a939e058786b6db7cf322b6ba78a43","user_type":"people","headline":"且听我胡说八道！","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560702729","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545880565,"updated_time":1545880565,"extras":"","is_copyable":false,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":8,"content":"\u003cp\u003e惊闻近日网络上有大量沙雕网友玩梗高中生网友证明“哥德巴赫猜想”，我深感痛惜！我曾有幸在2016年看过大数学家陈景润先生为《初等数论》一书写的序言，好不欢喜(两手翻花)。看着网友们的恶搞，你们好笑我是笑不出来，我这个眼泪在肚子里，我笑不出来。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e数学不是胡学，哥猜不是乱猜。\u003cbr\u003e哥德巴赫猜想并非不能证明，我研究哥猜20年了，大大小小的问题我都研究，我太了解它了！\u003cbr\u003e我刚刚打开知乎的时候，还有个知友问我，哥德巴赫猜想到底能不能证明啊？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不懂数学的网友还在笑，我是笑不出来。\u003cbr\u003e有的网友一看到“哥德巴赫猜想”，第一反应“哇，太难了！”这怎么行呢？见到这些世界级的数学难题，尤其需要勇于证明，从精神上藐视它。\u003cbr\u003e我们说一个学过数学的人不敢向世界级数学难题发起挑战是可悲的，有了挑战的勇气不能把它证明就是可耻的。\u003cbr\u003e我看有些学数学的，学神竟然和学霸谈起了恋爱，学霸叫学神叫“婶婶”，学神叫学霸叫“爸爸”，婶侄不分，父妻颠倒。\u003cbr\u003e这样的关系是乱伦的！是要给所有学数学的人谢罪的！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e喜闻一位高中生最近要在知乎上发表证明“哥德巴赫猜想”的论文，祝贺这位同学，这与这位同学长期的勤奋研究是分不开的。说到勤奋，我就想到正在网上认真学习研究“留学”勤奋写论文的我。今年下半年，“留学”研究会亲自举办的第一届“留学”生毕业典礼即将举行，我将作为第一届“留学”毕业生代表出席此次典礼，并认真发表关于“留学”研究的诸多感悟。生活学习两开花，弘扬“留学”文化，希望大家多多参加。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560396125,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"c5afca4748da16306298ab39f53fe830","url_token":"da-li-ya-wo-bo-yi","name":"达莉娅沃波依","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-549ed9bfe1448bc096e8d4993312bda3_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-549ed9bfe1448bc096e8d4993312bda3_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/c5afca4748da16306298ab39f53fe830","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560396125","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545834496,"updated_time":1545834496,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":13,"content":"\u003cp\u003e不要害怕别人说什么，有梦就去追\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e很大程度上众人都是抱着看笑话的心态来的，我也一样，但很不幸的是数学这门学科从初等到高等，发展的历史上充斥着偶然性，我怕你真的才华横溢别的不怎么行，偏偏把哥猜给试出来了，这就搞得我们很尴尬，岂不是打脸了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e所以呢，大家都在看着，你1月1号证出个啥，如果证成了，那别说清北了，哈佛mit绝大多数数学教授在你面前就是个弟弟。可你要证失败了，那就是成民科了，劝你老早回去继续复习，清北真的只是由高考分数决定的，而证实这种东西需要的天才和努力是任何大学都没法比的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e可你要是在营销涨粉，我十几个知乎号到时候追着喷的你 都不认识\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cvoteup_count%2Ccontent\u0026limit=20\u0026offset=180\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cvoteup_count%2Ccontent\u0026limit=20\u0026offset=140\u0026sort_by=default","totals":1823}}
